/target/
crates/guicons-build/tests/fixtures/*/target/
*.snap.new
# guicons-net's runtime cache dir (fetched iconify icons/collections) - can
# show up under any crate/fixture whose tests exercise it, not just the
# ones listed here before. Doesn't affect the handful of files already
# committed under a fixture's .cache/ on purpose (as pre-seeded offline
# test data) - .gitignore never untracks what's already tracked.
.cache/
ide-plugin/build/
ide-plugin/.gradle/
ide-plugin/.idea/
ide-plugin/.intellijPlatform/
ide-plugin/.kotlin/
